OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day, with some evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. The cloud will be thickening
OL,8,Ffrom the west to bring some outbreaks
OL,9,Fof rain overnight, which could be
OL,10,Flocally heavy on western hills.
OL,11,FFreshening winds. A mild night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA band of rain, locally heavy,
OL,14,Fwill be moving eastwards across all
OL,15,Fparts during the morning. Becoming
OL,16,Fdrier and brighter into the afternoon,
OL,17,Falthough a few showers are possible.
OL,18,FBreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
